01:49.400 --> 01:52.600
NOW I KNOW HE PAYS YOU FOR YOUR
SOUTH-OF-THE-BORDER SPIRIT,

01:52.900 --> 01:54.200
BUT LET'S GIVE DANIEL
A BREAK.

01:54.200 --> 01:55.800
BUT HE'S FINE.
HE COULD TOTALLY DO--

01:55.800 --> 01:58.100
OKAY, PEOPLE,????

01:58.100 --> 01:59.100
