BECOMING A WOMAN.

02:14.400 --> 02:15.200
LOOK AT HER.

02:16.200 --> 02:17.800
SHE'S BEEN DOING THAT
ALL NIGHT.

02:20.000 --> 02:22.700
AS FAR AS ALEXIS KNOWS,
WE'RE A HAPPY FAMILY.

02:22.700 --> 02:24.600
SHE DOESN'T KNOW
MOM AND DAD ARE DIVORCED.

02:24.600 --> 02:26.600
SHE DOESN'T KNOW MOM
ESCAPED FROM PRISON,

02:26.600 --> 02:28.400
OR WAS IN PRISON,
FOR THAT MATTER.

02:30.200 --> 02:31.100
BETTY?

02:31.200 --> 02:34.000
SORRY. I WAS JUST TRYING
TO PUT MYSELF IN HER SHOES.

02:34.300 --> 02:35.400
OKAY,
ARE YOU READY TO GO?

02:35.400 --> 02:37.500
NO, NO, NO, NO. I CAN'T.
I GOTTA STAY WITH HER.

02:37.600 --> 02:39.600
I'M THE REASON SHE'S HERE
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

02:39.600 --> 02:43.900
WHAT? NO. DANIEL, WILHELMINA HAS
BEEN RUNNING "MODE" BY HERSELF.

02:43.900 --> 02:45.700
SHE HASN'T TAKEN
ANY OF YOUR CHANGES,

02:45.700 --> 02:46.900
AND SHE WROTE
THE LETTER FROM THE EDITOR.

02:46.900 --> 02:48.100
THE ISSUE SHIPS TOMORROW.

02:48.100 --> 02:49.600
DON'T YOU AT LEAST
WANT TO SIGN OFF ON THE BOOK?

02:49.600 --> 02:52.000
SEE, THAT'S ANOTHER THING.
HOW I AM SUPPOSED TO TELL ALEXIS

02:52.000 --> 02:54.200
OUR FATHER
IS MARRYING WILHELMINA?

02:54.300 --> 02:57.400
SO THAT'S A YES
ON SEEING THE BOOK?
YEAH, GET THE BOOK.

02:59.800 --> 03:00.800
