IN THE MIRROR.

03:51.800 --> 03:53.600
MORE THAN USUAL?
YEAH.

03:53.600 --> 03:55.800
OH.
I JUST WISH
I GOT TO KNOW HER BETTER.

03:55.800 --> 03:56.900
YEAH, YEAH, AND I WISH

03:56.900 --> 03:58.800
I GOT TO KNOW MARLON BRANDO
BEFORE HE GOT FAT,

03:58.800 --> 04:00.500
