TO WHAT'S IMPORTANT HERE?

04:01.000 --> 04:04.800
THERE'S A FEY SOMMERS ESTATE
OUT THERE WITH YOUR NAME ON IT.

04:05.200 --> 04:07.100
HAVE YOU HEARD
FROM THE LAWYERS YET?

04:07.200 --> 04:09.500
