LATER TODAY.

04:09.500 --> 04:12.300
JUST WAITING TO HEAR
FROM THE PROBATE JUDGE.

04:20.600 --> 04:23.300
MOM, ALL THE BOXES
ARE STILL HERE.

04:23.300 --> 04:25.100
YEAH, I KNOW.
I'M STILL GOING THROUGH THEM.

04:25.100 --> 04:28.500
YOUR FATHER HAD
A LOT OF GREAT STUFF AT HIS APARTMENT,
LIKE THESE.

04:28.900 --> 04:30.200
YOU CAN'T FIND THESE
ANYWHERE.

04:30.200 --> 04:33.400
MOM, WE'RE IN QUEENS.
YOU CAN FIND THOSE <i>EVERYWHERE.</i>

04:33.400 --> 04:35.400
THEY WERE YOUR FATHER'S.
WE'RE KEEPING THEM.

04:38.600 --> 04:41.100
HERE'S YOUR LUNCH
FOR YOUR FIRST DAY AT "MODE,"

04:41.100 --> 04:42.900
MR. BIG SHOT INTERN!

04:42.900 --> 04:45.000
YOU WANT ME
TO <i>BRING</i> MY LUNCH?

04:45.300 --> 04:47.900
MOM,
THE FAMOUS "MODE" CAFETERIA?

04:47.900 --> 04:50.500
WHERE NAOMI CAMPBELL HAD
A TUNA MELT AND A MELTDOWN?

04:50.900 --> 04:52.300
