05:39.500 --> 05:40.800
RELEASE, DWAYNE.

05:43.900 --> 05:46.300
WHOA! EXCUSE ME!
WHAT DO YOU WANT, BETTY?

05:46.800 --> 05:49.500
I WAS JUST... COMING
TO GET THE BOOK

05:49.500 --> 05:51.000
SO DANIEL
COULD SIGN OFF ON IT.

05:51.000 --> 05:53.100
TELL DANIEL THE ISSUE
WILL BE FILLED

05:53.100 --> 05:55.800
WITH PRETTY GIRLS
WEARING SKIMPY LITTLE DRESSES.

05:55.800 --> 05:57.000
THAT'S ALL HE CARES ABOUT
ANYWAY.

05:57.000 --> 05:58.700
BUT I THINK THAT HE REAL--
BYE, BETTY.

05:58.700 --> 05:59.800
BUT HE REAL--
GOOD-BYE, BETTY.

05:59.800 --> 06:00.600
I KNOW THAT--
DWAYNE.

06:00.600 --> 06:03.300
OKAY, OKAY.
I'M LEAVING.

06:05.000 --> 06:07.200
UH, CONFIRM MY LUNCH
WITH NORA EPHRON

06:07.200 --> 06:09.900
AND MAKE SURE DWAYNE
GETS A SET OF MY HOUSE KEYS.

06:18.600 --> 06:19.700
MARC...
OH.

06:19.700 --> 06:21.100
YOU KNOW DANIEL
NEEDS TO SEE THE BOOK

06:21.100 --> 06:22.100
BEFORE IT GOES
TO THE PRINTER.

06:22.100 --> 06:23.400
COME ON.
PLEASE. THIS IS MY JOB.

06:23.400 --> 06:24.800
COULDN'T I JUST BORROW IT
FOR, LIKE, AN HOUR?

06:24.800 --> 06:27.300
GET AWAY FROM MY DESK, OR I'LL ???

06:29.000 --> 06:30.500
