06:37.400 --> 06:38.500
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

06:38.500 --> 06:41.000
HE HASN'T EVEN SEEN THEM!
OOPS.

06:41.800 --> 06:43.400
NOW I REALLY NEED
TO SEE THAT BOOK.

06:43.400 --> 06:45.100
LOOK, IT'S ????

06:45.100 --> 06:46.600
SO I COULDN'T
GIVE IT TO YOU

06:46.600 --> 06:48.200
EVEN IF I WANTED TO,
WHICH I DON'T.

06:48.200 --> 06:50.900
OH, DWAYNE.
IT'S A KEY. DON'T EAT IT.

