08:16.100 --> 08:18.100
BUT, YOU KNOW, WHATEVER.

08:19.100 --> 08:21.200
HENRY,
IT'S OKAY TO BE EXCITED.

08:21.900 --> 08:23.000
I REALLY AM.

08:23.000 --> 08:25.500
THERE'S SOMETHING
ABOUT BECOMING A FATHER.

08:25.600 --> 08:27.100
YOU KNOW, I COULD WORK
MY WHOLE LIFE

08:27.100 --> 08:28.400
AND NEVER BE
THE BEST ACCOUNTANT,

08:28.400 --> 08:31.200
BUT MAYBE I-I CAN BE
THE BEST DAD.

08:32.600 --> 08:33.799
I THINK YOU WILL BE.

08:35.900 --> 08:37.700
LISTEN,
THE REASON I'M HERE...

08:38.100 --> 08:39.100
UH-HUH.

08:39.100 --> 08:41.200
