A GREAT JOB IN TUCSON,

08:41.799 --> 08:43.500
AND THE MEADE HEALTH INSURANCE
WOULD COVER

08:43.500 --> 08:45.400
ALL THE MEDICAL EXPENSES
FOR THE BABY, SO--

08:45.400 --> 08:48.300
OH. SO YOU'RE COMING
BACK TO WORK.

08:48.300 --> 08:49.600
ONLY IF IT'S OKAY
WITH YOU, BETTY.

08:49.600 --> 08:51.500
IF YOU THINK IT'S A PROBLEM,
I'LL TURN DOWN THE JOB,

08:51.500 --> 08:53.200
BECAUSE I KNOW,
IT--IT MIGHT BE WEIRD.

08:53.200 --> 08:55.000
NO!
NO?

08:55.300 --> 08:56.800
I MEAN "NO"

08:56.800 --> 08:57.900
